<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207352>
    bibo:endPage "62" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "58" ;
    bibo:volume "2802" ;
    dc:creator "Pike, Keith S.; Starý, Petr; Graf, George; Raworth, David A.; Mathur, Sneh; Tanigoshi, Lynell K.; Murray, Todd" ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "A new Aphidius Nees (Hymenoptera, Braconidae, Aphidiinae) of Ericaphis fimbriata (Richards) (Hemiptera, Aphididae) and key to parasitoids of blueberry aphid in the Pacific Northwest" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207355> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207355>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Aphidius spp. parasitoids of the blueberry aphid. Aphidius ericaphidis sp. nov. (female): a, forewing; b – c, propodeum showing variation in carina; d, petiole; g, genitalia. Aphidius vaccinii (female): e, petiole. Aphidius ervi (female): f, petiole." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207355/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

